item.title: CVE-2023-35016|2024-10-11T19:11:23.390Z -- ibm -- security%20verify%20governance%2C%20identity%20manager
item.description: IBM Security Verify Governance, Identity Manager 10.0 could allow a remote attacker to traverse directories on the system. An attacker could send a specially crafted URL request containing "dot dot" sequences (/../) to view arbitrary files on the system. IBM X-Force ID: 257772.
